docs.text: Hi! I'm [Your Name], a passionate individual always eager to learn, explore, and create. Here's a little about me:

docs.text: I'm currently pursuing my Integrated M.Sc. in Chemistry at Manonmaniam Sundaranar University, Tamil Nadu. My research interests lie in Biochemistry and I'm aspiring to make impactful contributions in this field.
